# increase-score

## Feature

Increases the computer or player score

## Acceptance Criteria

### Scenario: Player misses the pong ball

  Given game in progress and computer move is successful
player plays next move

  When player plays moves and paddle misses pong ball

  Then computer score increase by 1

### Scenario: Computer misses pong ball

  Given game in progress and player move is successful
computer plays next move

  When computer plays moves and paddle misses pong ball

  Then computer score increase by 1
